### TechSolve API — REST Client test file
### Install "REST Client" extension, then click "Send Request" above each block

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001/api

# ── Services ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all services
GET {{baseUrl}}/services
Accept: application/json

###

### Get service by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/services/custom-software-development
Accept: application/json

# ── Blog ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get published blog posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog?page=1&pageSize=9
Accept: application/json

###

### Get blog post by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/blog/angular-19-signals-complete-guide
Accept: application/json

# ── Enquiry ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Submit enquiry
POST {{baseUrl}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Rajiv Mehta",
  "email": "rajiv@example.com",
  "phone": "+91 98765 43210",
  "company": "Acme Corp",
  "serviceSlug": "custom-software-development",
  "serviceName": "Custom Software Development",
  "message": "We need a custom ERP system built for our manufacturing unit. Looking for a senior team to handle the full project.",
  "sourcePageUrl": "http://localhost:4200/services/custom-software-development"
}

###

### Get enquiry by ticket ID (replace ticket ID after submitting above)
GET {{baseUrl}}/enquiry/TS-202501-ABC123
Accept: application/json

# ── WhatsApp Tracking ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Track WhatsApp click
POST {{baseUrl}}/whatsapptracking/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "test-session-001",
  "pageUrl": "http://localhost:4200/services",
  "pageTitle": "Our Services",
  "serviceSlug": "web-application-development",
  "serviceName": "Web Application Development",
  "clickSource": "services-page"
}

###

### Get WhatsApp analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/whatsapptracking/analytics?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-12-31
Accept: application/json
